title: Monday's girls' volleyball roundup: Perkiss leads William Penn past Harrisburg
text:
Posted: 10/19/2015 10:42:12 PM EDT 
Here are Monday's York/Adams girls' volleyball results. Check back often for updates. 
WILLIAM PENN 3, HARRISBURG 1 >> Emoni Perkiss crushed nine kills and two aces to lead the Bearcats to their second win of the season at home, 25-23, 25-27, 25-16, 25-23. 
Cheynne Bradford chipped in six kills for William Penn, and Keishla Ortiz dished out 19 assists. William Penn def. Harrisburg, 25-23, 25-27, 25-16, 25-23 at William Penn 
Harrisburg stats — Jazmyne Davis (10 assists, 3 aces), Deaubre Brock (6 kills, 3 aces). 
William Penn stats — Cheynne Bradford (6 kills, 1 ace, 5 digs), Emoni Perkiss (9 kills, 1 blocks, 2 aces, 7 digs), Jae Fitch (3 kills, 1 block, 2 aces), Nicheska Vigo (2 kills, 2 digs), Keishla Ortiz (1 kill, 19 assists), Diaja Aiken (2 assists, 4 aces). 
JV Score — William Penn def. Harrisburg, 26-24, 19-25, 15-12. 
JAMES BUCHANAN 3, LITTLESTOWN 0 >> The Rockets swept the Thunderbolts on the road, 25-22, 25-18, 25-21. 
Littlestown's Emily Staub had 21 assists to go with four aces, 2 kills and 13 digs. James Buchanan def. Littlestown, 25-22, 25-18, 25-21 at Littlestown 
James Buchanan stats — No stats available 
Littlestown stats — Emily Staub (21 assists 4 aces, 2 kills, 1 block, 13 digs), Vickie Skillman (1 ace, 13 digs, 2 kills, 1 block), Hanna Riley (1 ace, 5 digs, 4 kills), Kayley Ambrose (2 aces, 2 digs), Jillian Persing (13 digs), Mariah Hymiller (3 digs), Peyton Motter (1 dig, 1 kill), Alex Morrisset (1 dig), Brenna Feser (5 kills), Maggy Senseney (4 kills), Erin Plummer (3 kills). Advertisement 
JV Score — Littlestown def. James Buchanan, 25-16, 20-25, 15-11. 
BERMUDIAN SPRINGS 3, BOILING SPRINGS 0 >> Madyson Whitcomb drilled eight kills to lead the Eagles to the home sweep, 25-10, 25-12, 25-16. 
Gabby Emeigh chipped in 15 assists and two aces. Bermudian Springs def. Boiling Springs, 25-10, 25-12, 25-16 at Bermudian Springs 
Boiling Springs stats — No stats available. 
Bermudian Springs stats — Haley Dull (3 aces, 6 digs), Gabby Emeigh (2 aces, 2 blocks, 15 assists), Jenna Rohrbaugh (4 aces, 5 digs), Madyson Whitcomb (2 blocks, 8 kills, 2 aces), Miki Seifert (4 aces, 4 digs). 
JV Score — Bermudian Springs def. Boiling Springs, 25-14, 25-7.
